thread.title: Jolinda Henderson

author: Jolinda Henderson
title: Jolinda Henderson
text: I was really happy to find the pineapple licorice I was looking for. I am sad to say I probably won't order the licorice again because the item cost $17.70 and they charge $14 for shipping!! The post office has the "if it fits it ships" boxes a lot cheaper than $14 and it's not worth it to spend as much for the shipping as the item itself.
